name: Best project in Side
short_description:
Consists of 72 units allocated in 4 blocks.Welcome to a 21st Century sanctuary inspired by local history in an up-market neighbourhood. A cutting edge design complements outdoor living with generous private gardens and large roof terraces by seamlessly weaving together indoor and outdoor spaces.
Nympheum, located next to Sides unspoilt green belt and the dazzling East beach, is a unique residential project conceptualized to achieve a high level of architectural design excellence.
